          .col-md-6
            .panel.panel-default
                .panel-heading
                  .panel-h-icon
                    i.icon-bar-chart
                  | 单位价格对比图
                .panel-body#echarts-4(style="height:228px;")
          .col-md-6
            .panel.panel-default
                .panel-heading
                  .panel-h-icon
                    i.icon-inbox
                  | 各种材料成本占总成本比例
                .panel-body#echarts-5(style="height:228px;")
      .col-md-5
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            .panel-h-icon
              i.icon-signal
            | 参考消息
          .panel-body
            #echarts-1(style="height:260px;")
            +table({thead:['商品名称', '数值','幅度','解读'],border:false,count:7})(class="table-hover table-red border-b")
              tr
